data.meta_description:
vd_v_isuals on May 13, 2021: "Minister of State Mark Eyskens - the man, the myth, the legend.
Mark Eyskens worked as minister of Finance, Foreign Affairs and briefly took office as Prime Minister of Belgium in 1981.
(Needless to say, I was very nervous when developing this film roll because the stakes were so high.. Proud of the end result!)
Shot on @Hasselblad with @kodak 400TX and developed with Kodak D-76.
